README

The Display-O-Tron is a stylish and capable 3x16 character display with RGB backlights and LED bar graph.

Learn more: https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/display-o-tron-hat
For example scripts run: `curl -sS get.pimoroni.com/displayotron | bash`

IMPORTANT

The Display-O-Tron requires both i2c and spi.
To enable run `curl get.pimoroni.com/i2c | bash`
as well as `curl get.pimoroni.com/spi | bash`
or use raspi-config and reboot your Raspberry Pi.
